original_request:
I need to analyze our VA ambulance trip data from 2023 to identify
    which trips we could have captured in-house versus contracted out.
    Then build a simple dashboard so leadership can explore the results
    interactively by month and trip type.

structured_spec.title: VA Ambulance Trip Analysis
structured_spec.description: Perform a data analysis of the 2023 VA ambulance trip dataset to classify each trip as potentially handled in‑house or contracted out, then create a simple interactive dashboard that allows leadership to explore the results by month and trip type.
structured_spec.business_goal: Enable leadership to identify cost‑saving opportunities by understanding which ambulance trips could be managed in‑house versus outsourced.
deliverables: Classification logic and labeled dataset (in‑house vs contracted)
Analytical report summarizing findings and recommendations
Interactive web dashboard (e.g., PowerBI, Tableau, or custom web app) with filters for month and trip type
success_criteria: Dashboard accessible to leadership with correct breakdowns by month and trip type
Classification results validated against business rules with >95% accuracy on sample review
Dashboard loads and updates within 2 seconds for typical queries
All deliverables handed over with complete documentation
